==English==
===Etymology===
Old French ''[[dromadaire]]'' from Late Latin ''[[dromedarius]]'' "kind of camel" from Latin ''[[dromas]]'' (genitive ''dromadis''), from Greek [[δρομάς]] [[κάμηλος]] ''dromas kamelos'' "running camel" from [[δρόμος]] ''dromos'' "a race course.

